Mamelodi Sundown’s Hlompho Kekana and Kaizer Chiefs duo Lebogang Manyama and Samir Nurkovic will battle it out for the Goal of the Season award. This after the trio's stunning goals were voted as the as the three  best goals of the 2019/20 Absa Premiership season. The three goals were selected amongst seven others in a public vote. Kekana's strike came against Cape Town City in August 2019. Manyama's goal came in the Soweto derby back in February while his teammate Nurkovic's goal was against Bloemfontein Celtic in December last year. The winning goal will be announced at the PSL Awards on Thursday.